newsitem.title: USA: U.S. soyoil weekly export sales highlights--USDA.
newsitem.headline: U.S. soyoil weekly export sales highlights--USDA.

text.p: USDA soyoil weekly export sales highlights in latest reporting week:
Net sales of 2,000 MT were the result of increases for Brazil (1,300 MT), Singapore (1,000 MT), and Haiti (1,000 MT) being partially offset by reductions of 1,300 MT for unknown destinations.
Exports of 3,100 MT were to Brazil (1,300 MT), Jamaica (1,000 MT), and Costa Rica (800 MT).
